Class TrackLayout

  • java.lang.Object
    • Piece.track.TrackLayout
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Spiralable

    public class TrackLayout
extends java.lang.Object
implements Spiralable
    This class managed a specific sequence of Piece.track segments. Tracks are added male end first. The Track Layout object can also generate spirals.
